entry.def: If something whizzes somewhere, it moves there very fast.

example.ex: Stewart felt a bottle whizz past his head...
example.tran: 斯图尔特感觉有个瓶子从他头上嗖地一下飞了过去。

entry.def: If you are a whizz at something, you are very good at it.

example.ex: Simon's a whizz at card games.
